219
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:20,800
- Better luck next time.
- Better luck, Burt.

220
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:26,099
There you go.

221
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:30,100
- Well, thanks, love.
- Careful, its hot.

222
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:33,699
Well, at least I gave them
a good run for their money.

223
00:17:33,700 --> 00:17:36,399
On the downward leg anyway.

224
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:39,934
